== Introduction ==

The Stemfie Workbench is an [[External_workbenches|external workbench]] aimed at implementing a parametric set of parts for the [https://www.stemfie.org/ Stemfie project].

[[File:Stemfie_WB.jpg|Stemfie Workbench set of parts|700px]]

== Installing ==

The Stenfie workbench is not bundled with the default FreeCAD package, but can easily be installed via the [[Image:Std_AddonMgr.svg|24px]] [[Std_AddonMgr|Addon Manager]]. Invoke it from {{MenuCommand|Tools → [[Std_AddonMgr|Addons Manager]]}}. The Stemfie workbench code is [https://github.com/bilbaomakers/StemfieWB hosted and developed on github] and can also be installed manually by copying it into FreeCAD's {{FileName|MOD}} directory. 

